For Windows Binaries:

    Start powershell in administrator and run 'install.bat' (if prompted type 'Y')
    Then restart powershell and run 'make -f Windows.mk install INSTALL_DIR="%"' replacing % with where you want to install RLLUtils

    To uninstall run 'make -f Windows.mk uninstall INSTALL_DIR="%"' replacing % with where you installed RLLUtils

To Build Sources (Requires GnuWin32):

    Start powershell in administrator and run 'make install INSTALL_DIR="%"' replacing % with where you want to install RLLUtils

    To uninstall run 'make uninstall INSTALL_DIR="%"' replacing % with where you installed RLLUtils
